" - [#2]: A. A. Rasyid, T. Hidayat, and W. Orchiston. Star patterns in Mandar navigation. In W. Orchiston and M. N. Vahia, editors, Exploring the History of Southeast Asian Astronomy, pages 549–564. Springer, Cham, 2021.\n"
